headline: Is Deere (DE) Still Attractive After Its Strong 1 Year Share Price Run?
summary: If you are wondering whether Deere's share price still offers value at current levels, the key question is how the market is pricing its future cash flows and assets today. Over the past year, Deere's share price has moved to US$488.08, with returns of 4.6% over 7 days, 4.1% over 30 days, 4.6% year to date and 21.1% over 1 year. The 3 year and 5 year returns sit at 15.8% and 76.4% respectively. Recently, attention around Deere has centered on how the company is positioned within capital...
